author: Chris Pleasance For Daily Mail Australia
title: Ross Cameron claims Turnbull 'is finished' over Trump call | Daily Mail Online
text: 'Turnbull is finished': Former Liberal minister says PM's clash with Trump will end his reign - and claims 'too many selfies with Obama' enraged the new President Donald Trump allegedly blasted Malcolm Turnbull during their first phone call New President called it 'the worst call by far' and hung up after 25 minutes Ross Cameron said the Australian Prime Minister laid the groundwork for failure with 'a series of blunders and miscalculations' going back to last year Said taking selfies with Obama, donating government money to the Clinton Foundation, and saying he would 'go it alone' after TTP collapsed were to blame Published: 04:44 GMT, 2 February 2017 | Updated: 08:03 GMT, 2 February 2017 470 shares
